{"tid":1324120,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點會有人有興趣同陌生人keep chat?","createTime":"2019-07-16T12:58:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T16:24:29.000Z","uid":207336,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"13756b20b6d08d121c3c78713bb5b36dd6e0eb33","tid":1324120,"uid":207336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:58:36.000Z","msg":"有時見到啲人話交友app/網上識人，甚至係條街度識人，我都會諗點解會對個三唔識七既人有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能話見人幾靚/講既topic有趣，但長遠黎講有咩好傾？又冇common fd，又唔係住附近，兩者之間又冇任何連繫 eg參加活動/返工，究竟點解會有興趣同對方keep chat，甚至再進一步發展？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec79c691d6d475f5fcf7a97bab003dd6a231017","tid":1324120,"uid":207336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:03:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e43821b882eab3bee8cc15a56c4a3d2dee57e8","tid":1324120,"uid":207336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:03:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b015dfa17e3cd351f96a9445d03dc81854234d0b","tid":1324120,"uid":156326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:11:59.000Z","msg":"9up吓 冇成本 冇左又唔心痛"},{"pid":"3ca94d80eb41a1f2e0a0478391d24d2c9e544ac6","tid":1324120,"uid":84172,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:35:24.000Z","msg":"就係同三唔識七既人講野先無負擔<br />\n反正大家都唔知大家係邊個"},{"pid":"acc5dfa620fa0045511c83a599b4e3dbc751492d","tid":1324120,"uid":207336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b015dfa17e3cd351f96a9445d03dc81854234d0b","tid":1324120,"uid":156326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:11:59.000Z","msg":"9up吓 冇成本 冇左又唔心痛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T13:52:28.000Z","msg":"但會keep住講野？"},{"pid":"f2e68f24754e527726df4d9387762e9c8c7679f3","tid":1324120,"uid":156326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"